metadata.name: Invictus Order Application #1
metadata.description:
The Sector Task Force has begun to assemble to discover the mystery of The Altar. Only Prismatians with a reflection will be enlisted into the Sector Task Force.

The Invictus Order Application is a soulbound token that acts as your on-chain proof of submission. The SBT art and metadata will automatically update when an application is accepted.

To submit an application to join the Invictus Order, click [here](https://www.invictusorder.com/). For more information about how the allowlist and SBT works, check out this [blog post](https://mirror.xyz/ironhills.eth/tI53g0xxPiaYu_3Vp8oZIqPCZCfpsUnq4lpvo_YId3U).

[Invictus Order Application Ownership Agreement](https://www.invictusorder.com/agreement)
